# <% .Name %>

Auto-scaffolded <% .Type %> service.

## Getting Started

<% if eq .Type "nodejs" %>```bash
npm install
npm start
```<% else if eq .Type "python" %>```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn src.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port <% .Port %> --reload
```<% else %>```bash
go run ./src/...
```<% end %>

## Endpoints

| Endpoint | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `GET /` | Root — returns service name and status |
| `GET /healthz` | Liveness probe |
| `GET /ready` | Readiness probe |<% if eq .Type "python" %>
| `GET /docs` | Swagger UI |
| `GET /openapi.json` | OpenAPI schema |<% end %>

## Running Tests

<% if eq .Type "nodejs" %>```bash
npm test
```<% else if eq .Type "python" %>```bash
pytest src/ -q
```<% else %>```bash
go test ./src/...
```<% end %>

## Local Development (Kind)

```bash
# http://<% .Name %>.idp.local
helm upgrade --install <% .Name %> ./helm/service-template \
  --namespace <% .Namespace %> \
  --values services/<% .Name %>/helm-values-local.yaml
```

## Deploying

Push to `main` to trigger CI/CD (GitHub Actions → GHCR → Helm deploy).
